#define DEFAULT_RECORD_FMT   (CLF_VERSION | CLF_RENAME)

Convert all records to a same format according to the caller's wishes.

Default is CLF_VERSION | CLF_RENAME. Add CLF_JOBID if explicitely requested.

Parameters:
rec The record to remap. It is expected to be big enough to properly handle the final format.
Returns:
1 if anything changed. 0 otherwise. Read the next changelog entry
Parameters:
priv Opaque private control structure
rech Changelog record handle; record will be allocated here
Returns:
0 valid message received; rec is set <0 error code 1 EOF
